<%= t("mailer.intro_name", name: @site.user.name) %>

Thank you for taking the time to evaluate SublimeVideo! We hope you're enjoying your trial.

This is a reminder that the <%= BusinessModel.days_for_trial - 1 %>-day free trial for <%= @site.hostname.presence || 'your site' %> expires in <%= pluralize(full_days_until_trial_end(@site), 'day') %> (on <%= l(@site.trial_end, format: :named_date) %>).

<% if @site.user.cc? %>
  Once the trial ends, we will automatically charge your credit card <%= display_amount(@site.plan.price) %> for your <%= @site.plan.title %> plan.

  If you don't want to activate your paid plan, you can downgrade your site to the Free plan here:

  https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/sites/<%= @site.token %>/plan/edit
<% else %>
  Since automatic charging will start at the end of this trial, please be sure to register a credit card to prevent any charging issue. You can do it on this page:

  https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/account/billing/edit
<% end %>

<% unless @site.user.billing_address_complete? %>
  Please also give us a valid billing address:

  https://<%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>/account/billing/edit
<% end %>

